Script started on 2016å¹´11æœˆ02æ—¥ æ˜ŸæœŸä¸‰ 17æ—¶10åˆ†06ç§’
]0;zpoint@zpoint-PC: ~/Desktop/Reading-Exercises-Notes/C++ Primer/3_String_Vectors_and_Arrays[01;32mzpoint@zpoint-PC[00m:[01;34m~/Desktop/Reading-Exercises-Notes/C++ Primer/3_String_Vectors_annd_Arrays[00m$ ./a.out
Input two string
ss
dd
After concatenated: ssdd
Now enter several strings seperate by new line
